INSERT INTO `wpah_posts` VALUES (7486,1,'2020-08-03 02:07:49','2020-08-03 02:07:49','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">The type of service I offer is typically a Wordpress website that is built on the Genesis Framework. I use Genesis for my own sites, and mostly for client sites as well. Genesis delivers a high quality wordpress website that is SEO friendly and optimised for speed. Your site should ideally load in under 3 seconds and use a minimal amount of plugins in order to achieve this, and this is a marker I aim for when delivering a new web project. You can read more about why I use Genesis for my projects<a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\"> </a><strong><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\">here</a>.</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before we get to the how\'s of building a web project, I\'d like to walk you through the process from start to finish so you know what to expect and how much involvement is required </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>1. Client Brief</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether I\'m speaking with a client online or face to face, that first meeting is really about gathering information. Tell me your story. Why you got into this particular business. What are your current challenges? What do you like and dislike about your current website? What functions are you looking for? This is a genuine discussion where we uncover your needs, and what service offering is best going to match those needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>2. Design </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After uncovering your needs at our first meeting, I will request any asset files you have and wish to use and begin working on a site mockup for you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For <strong>bigger</strong> projects, you will get a design system in <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/\">Figma.</a> Usually we\'d start with a home page mockup, and if you are happy with the layout, I will then create additional pages for your site as well as as the responsive version. Your site will then be built using my Genesis starter theme. Yes it is still a child theme for Genesis, but there are no inherited styles or content, its a bare bones starter theme that merely has functions and a basic codebase to work off. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For clients with a <strong>limited budget,</strong> I will create a one page style guide and you will receive a link to a staging domain where I will edit your existing Genesis child theme to match the styles and colours of the chosen child theme. There may be some modifications to your functions.php file, and perhaps some custom functions or custom post types but your site will not be highly modified. This is because you can basically modify a child theme to within an inch of its life, and heavy modifications of an existing child theme require just as much work as building a site from a starter theme. And the budget allocated to the project reflects the amount of work required. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->','Web Development','','inherit','closed','closed','','7432-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 02:07:49','2020-08-03 02:07:49','',7432,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7432-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7489,1,'2020-08-03 04:37:32','2020-08-03 04:37:32','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">The type of service I offer is typically a Wordpress website that is built on the Genesis Framework. I use Genesis for my own sites, and mostly for client sites as well. Genesis delivers a high quality wordpress website that is SEO friendly and optimised for speed. Your site should ideally load in under 3 seconds and use a minimal amount of plugins in order to achieve this, and this is a marker I aim for when delivering a new web project. You can read more about why I use Genesis for my projects<a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\"> </a><strong><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\">here</a>.</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before we get to the how\'s of building a web project, I\'d like to walk you through the process from start to finish so you know what to expect and how much involvement is required </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>1. Client Brief</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether I\'m speaking with a client online or face to face, that first meeting is really about gathering information. Tell me your story. Why you got into this particular business. What are your current challenges? What do you like and dislike about your current website? What functions are you looking for? This is a genuine discussion where we uncover your needs, and what service offering is best going to match those needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>2. Design </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After uncovering your needs at our first meeting, I will request any asset files you have and wish to use and begin working on a site mockup for you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For <strong>bigger</strong> projects, you will get a design system in <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/\">Figma.</a> Usually we\'d start with a home page mockup, and if you are happy with the layout, I will then create additional pages for your site as well as as the responsive version. Your site will then be built using my Genesis starter theme. Yes it is still a child theme for Genesis, but there are no inherited styles or content, its a bare bones starter theme that merely has functions and a basic codebase to work off. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For clients with a <strong>limited budget,</strong> I will create a one page style guide and you will receive a link to a staging domain where I will edit your existing Genesis child theme to match the styles and colours of the chosen child theme. There may be some modifications to your functions.php file, and perhaps some custom functions or custom post types but your site will not be highly modified. This is because you can basically modify a child theme to within an inch of its life, and heavy modifications of an existing child theme require just as much work as building a site from a starter theme. And the budget allocated to the project reflects the amount of work required. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>3. Development</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the phase where your design and your style guide will be converted into code. You will be sent a development link and your site is deployed to a staging domain. This will allow you to see how your site is coming to fruition, and allows for a collaborative process between us to make sure you are completely happy with the look and feel of your site, and also add in any business functions you may wish to have such as Paypal integration, Mailchimp integration, Zapier, Zen desk and so on. Your site will also be continuously backed up with version control on Github, so if changes are made and you wish to revert to a previous version of the site the option is there to do so. You will be asked to provide the content- that is the pages and what is written to explain your service offering. If you aren\'t comfortable doing this, or don\'t have time I can do it for you for an additional charge. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>4. Deploy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">After you have approved your site and content on the staging domain, I will deploy your site to your domain using FTP client and your C Panel. I personally use and recommend <strong><a href=\"https://ventraip.com.au/\">Ventra IP</a> </strong>for secure and fast wordpress hosting, and if you arrange the hosting through us I will be able to login to your C panel in future if you require backups or updates. If you don\'t wish to do this, you can purchase your own hosting plan and give me access for the deployment process. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>5. Marketing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A misconception that commonly occurs amongst clients is that once their website is up and running, their phone will ring off the hook and this couldn\'t be more untrue. Yes your website is there to present your service/product to the internet and yes it will capture emails and integrate to your marketing database. However: if you do nothing to market your business online via social media, google adwords/shopping, social media advertising, content marketing and so on you are not doing anything to actively promote your business. Subsequently your traffic will be low, and your conversion rate even lower. If you want to be successful online, and within a short time period as opposed to a slow burn over ten years, you should expect to spend 5-10 times more on marketing than you did for your web project. Marketing is never going to be one single thing, but a combination of content marketing, social media, paid search, paid advertising and networking. If you can do all of these things successfully you will see good results over time. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Web Development','','inherit','closed','closed','','7432-autosave-v1','','','2020-08-03 04:37:32','2020-08-03 04:37:32','',7432,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7432-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7488,1,'2020-08-03 04:37:28','2020-08-03 04:37:28','<!-- wp:par