r time. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You should offer the best possible content, for free. Good content is relevant to your audience, helpful to solve their problems and well researched. And when I say relevant that means don\'t post cat videos or personal photos to your social media channels when you\'re trying to build credibility. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You\'ll know you\'re crushing your content marketing goals when you are getting an increase in engagement on social, and increase in traffic to your website and an increase in people contacting you wanting to work together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">I will be posting more about this topic and content marketing methods in detail on my blog, but for anyone interested in outsourcing their content marketing I can offer help with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Explainer/animated videos </li><li>Content research</li><li>Content writing</li><li>Content planning/calendar </li><li>social media videos </li><li>social media posts</li><li>Email marketing content </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Please get in touch with me if you\'d like to know more about these services and would like a quote.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Content Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7430-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 05:05:28','2020-08-03 05:05:28','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7430-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7506,1,'2020-08-03 05:04:26','2020-08-03 05:04:26','<!-- wp:pullquote -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>\"Content isn\'t <strong>king</strong>, it\'s the <strong>kingdom</strong>\"</p><cite>-Leo Odden</cite></bloc