n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You should offer the best possible content, for free. Good content is relevant to your audience, helpful to solve their problems and well researched. And when I say relevant that means don\'t post cat videos or personal photos to your social media channels when you\'re trying to build credibility. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You\'ll know you\'re crushing your content marketing goals when you are getting an increase in engagement on social, and increase in traffic to your website and an increase in people contacting you wanting to work together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">I will be posting more about this topic and content marketing methods in detail, but methods I am working on for now include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7303,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/macbook-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7303\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Writing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I offer a premier content writing service for websites, emails, blogs and social media articles. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Explainer Videos</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Animated explainer videos for your website, online course, product or service. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7533,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Avatar-27-1024x621.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7533\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Explainer/animated videos </li><li>Content research</li><li>Content writing</li><li>Content planning/calendar </li><li>social media videos </li><li>social media posts</li><li>Email marketing content </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">This is not an exhaustive list. Marketing is an ever changing and rapidly growing industry, and trends will continue to come and go. The most important thing is being consist</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-layouts /-->','Content Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7430-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 06:35:52','2020-08-03 06:35:52','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7430-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7538,1,'2020-08-03 07:21:17','2020-08-03 07:21:17','{\n    \"sidebars_widgets[front-page-5]\": {\n        \"value\": [\n            \"text-10\"\n        ],\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2020-08-03 07:15:28\"\n    },\n    \"widget_media_image[20]\": {\n        \"value\": {\n            \"encoded_serialized_instance\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"\",\n            \"is_widget_customizer_js_value\": true,\n            \"instance_hash_key\": \"a0331e9334f0bef7939941fed0b65d93\"\n        },\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2020-08-03 07:15:28\"\n    },\n    \"widget_text[12]\": {\n        \"value\": [],\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1