g out to my personal mentor <a href=\"https://www.billerickson.net/\"><strong>Bill Erickson</strong></a> who is arguably one of the best Genesis developers out there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Why I use the Genesis Framework','','inherit','closed','closed','','7478-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 01:34:53','2020-08-03 01:34:53','',7478,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7478-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(580,1,'2018-07-18 06:59:43','2018-07-18 06:59:43','\n				\n								','Jon Paterson','\n				\n				Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.				','publish','closed','closed','','jon-paterson','','','2018-07-18 06:59:43','2018-07-18 06:59:43','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=team&amp;p=580',0,'team','',0),(581,1,'2018-07-18 07:00:32','2018-07-18 07:00:32','\n				\n								','Ramon Peypoch','\n				\n				Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.				','publish','closed','closed','','ramon-peypoch','','','2018-07-18 07:00:32','2018-07-18 07:00:32','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=team&amp;p=581',0,'team','',0),(582,1,'2018-07-18 07:01:37','2018-07-18 07:01:37','\n				\n								','Gene Stevens','\n				\n				Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.				','publish','closed','closed','','gene-stevens','','','2018-07-18 07:01:37','2018-07-18 07:01:37','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=team&amp;p=582',0,'team','',0),(583,1,'2018-07-18 07:02:11','2018-07-18 07:02:11','\n				\n								','Scott Chasin','\n				\n				Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.				','publish','closed','closed','','scott-chasin','','','2018-07-18 07:02:11','2018-07-18 07:02:11','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=team&amp;p=583',0,'team','',0),(7570,1,'2020-08-04 23:58:06','2020-08-04 23:58:06','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7519,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Ignoring-online-marketing-is-like-opening-a-business-and-not-telling-a-soul_-1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7519\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">When you visit a website that just has a basic service offering and a phone number what\'s your honest first impression? Do they seem trustworthy to you? Or at the very least, does anything on that site motivate you to take action in any way? The answer is most likely no. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Let me paint you a picture. Your cupboard falls off its hinge. You bought a new joiner and it kept coming out. You\'ve tried to fix it to no avail. So you google how to fix a cupboard join, and you find a helpful blog post from a local carpenter on how to fix the exact issue you\'re having. Except you\'re not a carpenter and your cupboard is still broken. Who are you going to call to fix it? The local carpenter with the helpful blog post who has gone out of his way to help you for free, or another carpenter who\'s website sits contentless? Who has built more trust and authority with you, the business with valuable content or the one with nothing? </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>The best way to build authority is to create high quality, educational content and continuing to do it over time. </p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">This is where the saying content is king comes from. Content is the defining difference between action and hesitation, or more bluntly between gaining and losing a sale. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You should offer the best possible content, for free. Good content is relevant to your audience, helpful to solve their problems and well researched. And when I say relevant that means don\'t post cat videos or personal photos to your social media channels when you\'re trying to build credibility. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You\'ll know you\'re crushing your content marketing goals when you are getting an increase in engagement on social, and increase in traffic to your website and an increase in people contacting you wanting to work together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">I will be posting more about this topic and content marketing methods in detail, but methods I am working on for now include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7565,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/green-chameleon-s9CC2SKySJM-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7565\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Writing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content writing for your website, blog, press releases and social media articles. All content is researched and proof read for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Explainer Videos</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Explainer or promotional videos for your website, online course or social media channels. All videos will have subtitles, and voiceover can be provided.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7533,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Avatar-27-1024x621.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7533\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7303,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/macbook-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7303\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Research</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content is usually planned on a calendar 6-12 months ahead. Content is researched, and set to auto publish from your site to your social channels. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-colu