for your ad spend. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My goal when conducting digital campaigns for clients, at the very least is to cover my cost. That is the money you as the client spends on hiring me to manage your marketing is offset by the increase in results you attain from hiring a professional. This effect is also compounded by the fact that you now have a lot more time that you were spending on marketing, to other facets of your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Google Analytics</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google analytics gives us the data for your web traffic, organic search, paid search, keyword ranking, click through traffic from social and external URL\'s. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7600,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/morning-brew-NrOUHQ2jHtU-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7600\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7592,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/stephen-phillips-hostreviews-co-uk-shr_Xn8S8QU-unsplash-1-1024x625.jpg\" alt=\"google adwords img alt\" class=\"wp-image-7592\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pay Per Click</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google adwords, Google shopping, Bing search and Duck Duck go advertisi