1024.jpg\" alt=\"iphone app screen img\" class=\"wp-image-7611\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>App advertising</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where relevant to your industry, advertising on apps of relational products and services can be an effective and somewhat cost efficient way to bring more traffic to your site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','Digital Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7436-revision-v1','','','2020-08-05 01:19:16','2020-08-05 01:19:16','',7436,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7436-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7617,0,'2020-08-05 05:38:52','2020-08-05 05:38:52','janeleeshian@yahoo.com.au\nJane LeeShian Whitehead','janeleeshian@yahoo.com.au','','publish','closed','closed','','janeleeshian-yahoo-com-au','','','2020-08-05 05:38:52','2020-08-05 05:38:52','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=flamingo_contact&#038;p=7617',0,'flamingo_contact','',0),(7618,0,'2020-08-05 01:48:46','2020-08-05 01:48:46','Jane LeeShian Whitehead\njaneleeshian@yahoo.com.au\nweb enquiry 1\ntest1\n1\n101.173.160.189\nMozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_15_6) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/84.0.4147.105 Safari/537.36\nhttps://alphaomegadigital.com.au/contact-2/\nAugust 5, 2020\n1:48 am\n7443\ncontact-2\nContact\nhttps://alphaomegadigital.com.au/contact-2/\nrdoRp9HioP\nheny.jon112@gmail.com\nAlpha Omega Digital\nMore than just websites\nhttps://alphaomegadigital.com.au\njaneleeshian@gmail.com','web enquiry 1','','publish','closed','closed','','web-enquiry-1','','','2020-08-05 01:48:46','2020-08-05 01:48:46','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=flamingo_inbound&p=7618',0,'flamingo_inbound','',0),(7619,1,'2020-08-05 01:53:31','2020-08-05 01:53:31','{\n    \"sidebars_widgets[front-page-3]\": {\n        \"value\": [],\n        \"type\": \