mage {\"id\":7284,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/web-development/\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/free-apple-macbook-mockup-1-1024x673.jpg\" alt=\"website dev img\" class=\"wp-image-7284\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/web-development/\">Web Development</a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/digitalmarketing/\">Digital Marketing</a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7607,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/digitalmarketing/\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/austin-distel-tLZhFRLj6nY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Facebook advertising image\" class=\"wp-image-7607\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2020-08-06 02:14:58','2020-08-06 02:14:58','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?page_id=7428',0,'page','',0),(7429,1,'2020-08-02 10:46:22','2020-08-02 10:46:22','','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','7428-revision-v1','','','2020-08-02 10:46:22','2020-08-02 10:46:22','',7428,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7428-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7430,1,'2020-08-02 21:49:22','2020-08-02 21:49:22','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7519,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Ignoring-online-marketing-is-like-opening-a-business-and-not-telling-a-soul_-1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7519\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">When you visit a website that just has a basic service offering and a phone number what\'s your honest first impression? Do they seem trustworthy to you? Or at the very least, does anything on that site motivate you to take action in any way? The answer is most likely no. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Let me paint you a picture. Your cupboard falls off its hinge. You bought a new joiner and it kept coming out. You\'ve tried to fix it to no avail. So you google how to fix a cupboard join, and you find a helpful blog post from a local carpenter on how to fix the exact issue you\'re having. Except you\'re not a carpenter and your cupboard is still broken. Who are you going to call to fix it? The local carpenter with the helpful blog post who has gone out of his way to help you for free, or another carpenter who\'s website sits contentless? Who has built more trust and authority with you, the business with valuable content or the one with nothing? </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>The best way to build authority is to create high quality, educational content and continuing to do it over time. </p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">This is where the saying content is king comes from. Content is the defining difference between action and hesitation, or more bluntly between gaining and losing a sale. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You should offer the best possible content, for free. Good content is relevant to your audience, helpful to solve their problems and well researched. And when I say relevant that means don\'t post cat videos or personal photos to your social media channels when you\'re trying to build credibility. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">You\'ll know you\'re crushing your content marketing goals when you are getting an increase in engagement on social, and increase in traffic to your website and an increase in people contacting you wanting to work together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">I will be posting more about this topic and content marketing methods in detail, but service available include: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7565,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/green-chameleon-s9CC2SKySJM-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7565\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Writing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content writing for your website, blog, press releases and social media articles. All content is researched and proof read for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Explainer Videos</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Explainer or promotional videos for your website, online course or social media channels. All videos will have subtitles, and voiceover can be provided.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7533,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Avatar-27-1024x621.png\" alt=\"explainer video img\" class=\"wp-image-7533\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7303,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/macbook-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7303\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Research</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Content is usually planned on a calendar 6-12 months ahead. Content is researched, and set to auto publish from your site to your social channels. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Social Media </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social media posts, advertising management, campaign management, response to comments and more. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7563,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/instagram-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"image of iphone instagam\" class=\"wp-image-7563\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7566,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/stephen-phillips-hostreviews-co-uk-3Mhgvrk4tjM-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7566\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Email Marketing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Custom made emails that reflect your brand, promote your sale and bring in revenue to your email list.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-layouts /-->','Content Marketing','','publish','closed','closed','','content-marketing','','','2020-08-05 01:02:59','2020-08-05 01:02:59','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?page_id=7430',0,'page','',0),(7431,1,'2020-08-02 21:49:22','2020-08-02 21:49:22','','Content Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7430-revision-v1','','','2020-08-02 21:49:22','2020-08-02 21:49:22','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7430-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7432,1,'2020-08-02 21:49:58','2020-08-02 21:49:58','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">The type of service I offer is typically a Wordpress website that is built on the Genesis Framework. I use Genesis for my own sites, and mostly for client sites as well. Genesis delivers a high quality wordpress website that is SEO friendly and optimised for speed. Your site should ideally load in under 3 seconds and use a minimal amount of plugins in order to achieve this, and this is a marker I aim for when delivering a new web project. You can read more about why I use Genesis for my projects<a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\"> </a><strong><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\">here</a>.</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before we get to the how\'s of building a web project, I\'d like to walk you through the process from start to finish so you know what to expect and how much involvement is required </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>1. Client Brief</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether I\'m speaking with a client online or face to face, that first meeting is really about gathering information. Tell me your story. Why you got into this particular business. What are your current challenges? What do you like and dislike about your current website? What functions are you looking for? This is a genuine discussion where we uncover your needs, and what service offering is best going to match those needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>2. Design </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After uncovering your needs at our first meeting, I will request any asset files you have and wish to use and begin working on a site mockup for you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For <strong>bigger</strong> projects, you will get a design system in <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/\">Figma.</a> Usually we\'d start with a home page mockup, and if you are happy with the layout, I will then create additional pages for your site as well as as the responsive version. Your site will then be built using my Genesis starter theme. Yes it is still a child theme for Genesis, but there are no inherited styles or content, its a bare bones starter theme that merely has functions and a basic codebase to work off. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For clients with a <strong>limited budget,</strong> I will create a one page style guide and you will receive a link to a staging domain where I will edit your existing Genesis child theme to match the styles and colours of the chosen child theme. There may be some modifications to your functions.php file, and perhaps some custom functions or custom post types but your site will not be highly modified. This is because you can basically modify a child theme to within an inch of its life, and heavy modifications of an existing child theme require just as much work as building a site from a starter theme. And the budget allocated to the project reflects the amount of work required. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>3. Development</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the phase where your design and your style guide will be converted into code. You will be sent a development link and your site is deployed to a staging domain. This will allow you to see how your site is coming to fruition, and allows for a collaborative process between us to make sure you are completely happy with the look and feel of your site, and also add in any business functions you may wish to have such as Paypal integration, Mailchimp integration, Zapier, Zen desk and so on. Your site will also be continuously backed up with version control on Github, so if changes are made and you wish to revert to a previous version of the site the option is there to do so. You will be asked to provide the content- that is the pages and what is written to explain your service offering. If you aren\'t comfortable doing this, or don\'t have time I can do it for you for an additional charge. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>4. Deploy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">After you have approved your site and content on the staging domain, I will deploy your site to your domain using FTP client and your C Panel. I personally use and recommend <strong><a href=\"https://ventraip.com.au/\">Ventra IP</a> </strong>for secure and fast wordpress hosting, and if you arrange the hosting through us I will be able to login to your C panel in future if you require backups or updates. If you don\'t wish to do this, you can purchase your own hosting plan and give me access for the deployment process. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>5. Marketing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A misconception that commonly occurs amongst clients is that once their website is up and running, their phone will ring off the hook and this couldn\'t be more untrue. Yes your website is there to present your service/product to the internet and yes it will capture emails and integrate to your marketing database. However: if you do nothing to market your business online via social media, google adwords/shopping, social media advertising, content marketing and so on you are not doing anything to actively promote your business. Subsequently your traffic will be low, and your conversion rate even lower. If you want to be successful online, and within a short time period as opposed to a slow burn over ten years, you should expect to spend 5-10 times more on marketing than you did for your web project. Marketing is never going to be one single thing, but a combination of content marketing, social media, paid search, paid advertising and networking. If you can do all of these things successfully you will see good results over time. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Web Development','','publish','closed','closed','','web-development','','','2020-08-03 04:37:28','2020-08-03 04:37:28','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?page_id=7432',0,'page','',0),(7433,1,'2020-08-02 21:49:58','2020-08-02 21:49:58','','Web Development','','inherit','closed','closed','','7432-revision-v1','','','2020-08-02 21:49:58','2020-08-02 21:49:58','',7432,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7432-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7434,1,'2020-08-02 21:50:12','2020-08-02 21:50:12','','Social media','','trash','closed','closed','','social-media__trashed','','','2020-08-05 01:20:56','2020-08-05 01:20:56','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?page_id=7434',0,'page','',0),(7435,1,'2020-08-02 21:50:12','2020-08-02 21:50:12','','Social media','','inherit','closed','closed','','7434-revision-v1','','','2020-08-02 21:50:12','2020-08-02 21:50:12','',7434,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7434-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7436,1,'2020-08-02 21:50:29','2020-08-02 21:50:29','<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7516,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Ignoring-online-marketing-is-like-opening-a-business-and-not-telling-a-soul_-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7516\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap {\"dropCapFontSize\":2} -->\n<div style=\"color:#32373c\" class=\"wp-block-atomic-blocks-ab-drop-cap drop-cap-letter ab-font-size-2 ab-block-drop-cap\"><div class=\"ab-drop-cap-text\"><p>The internet is such a big part of our lives now and it has completely changed the way in which we bank, shop, consume media and socialise. </p></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Newspaper and magazine have become mostly <a href=\"https://www.crikey.com.au/2020/05/04/australia-magazines-disruption-bauer/\">defunct</a> in Australia, as readership has dwindled and advertising costs have remained high; needless to say this means advertisers have been paying the same advertising rates for a lesser result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TV advertising has also taken a <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/digital-ad-spend-to-overtake-tv-in-2017-studies-find\">hit</a>; once considered the gold standard of effective advertising in Australia, ad free streaming services such as Netflix and Stan have drawn audiences away from mainstream TV. Audiences for years were frustrated with the increasing amount of ads on TV, but they tolerated it when no other options were available. Streaming services have provided a solution to this problem, thus creating a mass exodus from commercial TV. This applies to the embattled <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/news-corp-s-billion-dollar-write-down-for-foxtel#:~:text=News%20Corp%20has%20written%20down,nearly%20%24US1%20billion%20(AUD1.&amp;text=27%20billion%20(AUD3.,of%20%24US1%20billion%20(AUD1.\">Foxte</a>l as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These events mean Australian businesses are spending more money than ever on digital marketing: in 2017 we spent 3.43 billion advertising online, and in 2019 we spent a whopping <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/australian-brands-spent-9-4-billion-on-digital-ads-in-2019\">9.4 billion</a>, which is significantly higher than the previous forecast of 4.97 billion for <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/digital-ad-spend-to-overtake-tv-in-2017-studies-find\">2019</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Aside from the obvious fact that digital marketing is now more effective than traditional media, it also offers a degree of transparency. You no longer have to place an ad and cross your fingers it works for you, all of the data is readily available through the many digital analytics platforms so you know exactly how each dollar translates into web traffic, social media traffic, engagement and sales. I use <a href=\"https://databox.com/\">databox</a> to track all of these metrics with clients. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is one caveat to my previous statement though: although transparency and data are a surety in the digital age, none of those metrics are guaranteed to translate into sales for your business. This presents a problem to the everyday business owner who is running their own digital campaigns. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is a sense of achievement and the feeling of being in control; you\'re spending money and you can see its resulting in extra likes to your page, more followers, more traffic, more page views. There is really only one question to ask yourself  at this point:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>\"Are your current digital marketing efforts translating into sales?</p><p></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the answer is yes, then awesome keep doing what you\'re doing if you\'re happy with your figures. If the answer is no, then it\'s really time to engage with a professional to maximise the results you\'re getting for your ad spend. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My goal when conducting digital campaigns for clients, at the very least is to cover my cost. That is the money you as the client spends on hiring me to manage your marketing is offset by the increase in results you attain from hiring a professional. This effect is also compounded by the fact that you now have a lot more time that you were spending on marketing, to other facets of your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Google Analytics</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google analytics gives us the data for your web traffic, organic search, paid search, keyword ranking, click through traffic from social and external URL\'s. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7600,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/morning-brew-NrOUHQ2jHtU-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7600\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7592,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/stephen-phillips-hostreviews-co-uk-shr_Xn8S8QU-unsplash-1-1024x625.jpg\" alt=\"google adwords img alt\" class=\"wp-image-7592\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pay Per Click</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google adwords, Google shopping, Bing search and Duck Duck go advertising give us real world data on impressions, CTR, page views, revenue and references. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ads Manager</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Facebook ads manager allows us to create effective and budget controlled Facebook and Instagram campaigns, filtering demographics by age, location, occupation, previous page views and competitor views. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7607,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/austin-distel-tLZhFRLj6nY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Facebook advertising image\" class=\"wp-image-7607\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7613,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/neonbrand-GCQaYDCQwgc-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"app advertising img\" class=\"wp-image-7613\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>App advertising</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where relevant to your industry, advertising on apps of relational products and services can be an effective and somewhat cost efficient way to bring more traffic to your site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','Digital Marketing','','publish','closed','closed','','digitalmarketing','','','2020-08-05 02:00:02','2020-08-05 02:00:02','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?page_id=7436',0,'page','',0),(7437,1,'2020-08-02 21:50:29','2020-08-02 21:50:29','','Content creation','','inherit','closed','closed','','7436-revision-v1','','','2020-08-02 21:50:29','2020-08-02 21:50:29','',7436,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7436-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7438,1,'2020-08-02 21:51:45','2020-08-02 21:51:45',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','7438','','','2020-08-06 01:29:49','2020-08-06 01:29:49','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?p=7438',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(7615,1,'2020-08-05 02:36:05','2020-08-05 02:36:05','heny.jon112@gmail.com\nrdoRp9HioP','heny.jon112@gmail.com','','publish','closed','closed','','heny-jon112-gmail-com','','','2020-08-05 02:36:05','2020-08-05 02:36:05','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/heny-jon112-gmail-com/',0,'flamingo_contact','',0),(7440,1,'2020-08-02 21:51:45','2020-08-02 21:51:45',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','7440','','','2020-08-06 01:29:49','2020-08-06 01:29:49','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?p=7440',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(7441,1,'2020-08-02 21:51:45','2020-08-02 21:51:45',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','7441','','','2020-08-06 01:29:49','2020-08-06 01:29:49','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?p=7441',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(74