enesis easier. New releases of Genesis range from every few months to daily. You can view the changelog <a href=\"https://studiopress.github.io/genesis/changelog/\">here</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>From a professional standpoint, I know that when I run into development problems with Genesis, I have a variety of support options available. Those options range from logging a ticket with <a href=\"https://www.studiopress.com/\">Studiopress</a>, starting a thread in the community <a href=\"https://genesis.community/\">forum</a>, or even reaching out to my personal mentor <a href=\"https://www.billerickson.net/\">Bill Erickson</a> who is arguably one of the best Genesis developers out there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Why I use the Genesis Framework','','inherit','closed','closed','','7478-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 01:34:07','2020-08-03 01:34:07','',7478,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7478-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1429,1,'2017-12-17 03:26:59','2017-12-17 03:26:59','Genesis Simple FAQ is a plugin for the Genesis Framework to manage FAQ components via shortcodes.','What is the Genesis Simple FAQ plugin?','','publish','closed','closed','','faq-1','','','2017-12-17 03:26:59','2017-12-17 03:26:59','',0,'https://corporate-pro.dev/?post_type=gs_faq&amp;p=1351',0,'gs_faq','',0),(1484,1,'2017-11-19 23:48:50','2017-11-19 23:48:50','The Genesis Simple FAQ plugin is available on WordPress.org. <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/genesis-simple-faq/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Click here to download</a>.','Where can I download the Genesis Simple FAQ plugin?','','publish','closed','closed','','faq-5','','','2017-11-19 23:48:50','2017-11-19 23:48:50','',0,'https://corporate-pro.dev/?post_type=gs_faq&amp;p=51',0,'gs_faq','',0),(1485,1,'2017-11-19 23:49:01','2017-11-19 23:49:01','You are able to add the FAQ section to many locations on your website, including a front page widget section, your page content, or a 